  <brief_title>The Efficacy of Midazolam &amp; Ketamine Versus Midazolam &amp; Fentanyl for Sedation in Ambulatory Colonoscopies</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Soroka University Medical Center</agency>
